title: “Take Back Our Democracy”
content:
A 2 HOUR ELECTION DAY SPECIAL! REAL PROGRESSIVES SPEAK OUT! <!--more-->

  • Featuring Gary Null and Danny Schector Guest Panelists 1) Walt Thiessen; Freedom News Hour - Former Congress candidate and Libertarian author and supporter 2) Norman Solomon; Political Analysis - Nationally syndicated columnist for “Media Beat” (1992-2009) 3) Jon Rappoport; The Jon Rappoport Show - Freelance investigative journalist for over 20 years 4) David Swanson - One of the founders of ACORN, Kucinich Press Secretary (2008) 5) Glen Ford; Black Agenda Radio - Journalist and political activist for over 40 years and co-publisher of Black Agenda Report 6) Christiane Brown; The Solution Zone - Radio broadcaster and television writer/producer for over 20 years
